Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:02.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wiped out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.88,0:00:06.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But considering the tactic he used,\N I'm sure that Kanoichi-kun thought
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:09.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,there was a chance this would succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:14.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What? Isn't that a bit much to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:23.94,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention that he did tell\N Miyako-kun not to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:29.74,sign_610_6_Nerima,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H322E26&}Nerima
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.86,0:00:29.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're not obligated to lend\N Miyako-kun out to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:33.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,nor clean up the mess that you guys made.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:38.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how dangerous it is,\N but our hands our tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:39.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:42.20,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If we were to get jurisdiction over the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:44.31,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,then we may be able to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:45.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
