Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:31.50,Ep_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,550)}#11 "The Ears of Sand and the Guts of a New Employee"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:29.70,Default - Top,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone dealing with\N the cocoons was wiped out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:30.90,Default - Top,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:34.38,Default - Top,Fairies,0000,0000,0000,,She's mad, she's super mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:38.22,Default,Fairy,0000,0000,0000,,Manari-sama is mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:36.80,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:41.67,Default,Fairy,0000,0000,0000,,We can't make offerings!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:44.84,Default,Fairy,0000,0000,0000,,The Silkworm Princess is really angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:47.47,Default,Fairy,0000,0000,0000,,Now none of us can live here anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:49.16,Default,Fairies,0000,0000,0000,,Jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:52.62,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Offerings? What offerings?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:54.83,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,Offerings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:56.34,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what they said?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:57.86,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:02:59.92,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,This is really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:03.59,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, those cocoons were\N materials to make offerings to a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.85,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,A god?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.37,sign_4493_35_Senda_Reiji__Shi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Senda Reiji\N {\fs10\b0}Shinjuku Ward Office Nocturnal Community Relations Division
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.37,sign_4493_36_Incoming_call,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming call
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.12,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:16.88,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako-kun, have you ever\N heard of Oshira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.78,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,They're one of the kaikogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:21.76,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to be worse\N than handling demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:26.65,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,At least you can exorcise\N demons and deal with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:30.82,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,But mess with the gods of this\N country, and they'll curse you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:33.33,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:36.64,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we did piss them off quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:40.40,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,Worst case scenario, they might turn into\N tatarigami, and then we'll really be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.62,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's usually a ritual we can do
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:46.14,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,to appease the angered\N god before it comes to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:49.14,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,but those rituals have always\N been a bit complicated
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.98,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,and it's hard to communicate with...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:53.82,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:55.05,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:59.18,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,City Hall's asking us to settle\N things with the Another
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:01.05,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,using Miyako-kun's Ears of Sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.38,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,It's on the verge of becoming a tatarigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.83,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with putting\N Arata in danger like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:09.69,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:10.59,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:12.06,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:13.42,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,You—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:15.61,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's pretty scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:19.37,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm able to tell what's\N actually scary right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:24.17,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,If there's something I can\N do about this... I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:33.46,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.93,0:04:35.46,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:42.40,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Good. This is a perfect opportunity\N to make City Hall owe us one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:43.47,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:52.85,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,I knew there was a parent somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:54.73,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,I let my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:56.98,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,This is a kekkaiseki blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:00.81,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,It has the ability to kill Anothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:05.49,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,I can kill you with my own hands.\N You're just another insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:12.01,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you're\Ntrying to say, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.34,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,Can't move, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:23.19,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,You show up out of nowhere, wreck this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:25.04,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,and then have the nerve to hurt some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.81,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you things would get a clue already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:31.73,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,This place belongs to us humans now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:35.31,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,There's no place for Anothers like you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:44.32,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:46.12,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:48.51,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in you showing up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.25,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to wait, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:56.69,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you little—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:58.54,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hurt her any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.69,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,"Her"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:01.88,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,That's an Another! She's not human!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.46,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,Once I kill her, this will all be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.59,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.51,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,You just want to kill Anothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:11.27,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't going to solve anything!\N It's just going to create a bigger mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:12.33,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.39,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,And {\i1}you{\i0} can stay out of the way of {\i1}my{\i0} work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:17.32,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:18.82,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:23.16,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I getting a call at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:24.64,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,You should probably answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:28.28,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinjuku Ward Office?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.16,sign_9418_98_Emergency_Line__,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency Line #0
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.16,sign_9418_99_Incoming_Call,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming Call
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.16,sign_9418_100_Decline_the_call,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Decline the call \Nand send a message
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.16,sign_9418_101_Send_to_voicemai,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Send to voicemail
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:36.92,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kanoichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:40.37,Italics,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Heya, this is Senda from\N the Shinjuku Ward Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.67,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing on this line?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:46.02,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Could you let Miyako-kun and \Nmy crew handle the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:48.76,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,while you go rescue the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:51.38,Italics,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure you have no authority over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:52.68,Italics,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one in charge of this—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:55.30,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, about that... You're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:56.27,Italics,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:07:01.44,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,City Hall has let go of their jurisdiction over\N the Olympic Stadium for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:05.38,Italics,senda,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinjuku Ward Office Nocturnal\N Community Relations Division
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:07.04,Italics,senda,0000,0000,0000,,is now in charge of this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:09.27,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell authorized that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:13.07,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Number Zero of the Tokyo Nocturnal\N Special Ordinance Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:16.83,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,The governor... of Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:20.33,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,So yeah, this is now our jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:23.83,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't step out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.52,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:32.55,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,So what's someone as\N worthless as you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.50,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to free her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.47,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.48,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Manari-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:48.86,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,Seimei...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:52.18,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.86,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,What could you possibly want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:58.74,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to apologize for what\N the humans have done to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.51,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,You have some nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:11.84,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing that can undo\N what you humans have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:14.79,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,To think that half of them were burned...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:18.98,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,My poor, defenseless silk spinners\N that could do nothing but burn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.22,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,How mortifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:29.11,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,Those children didn't just\N produce silk to make cocoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:35.47,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,After they emerged, they would spin\N their own cocoons into the finest silk thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:39.94,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I had the remaining\N children continue to produce silk,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:42.45,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,there aren't enough to spin it into thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:49.13,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't depart by dawn, I won't\N make it in time for the Izumo festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:55.84,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,Without silk to offer to the gods,\N we cannot receive the power of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:09:01.10,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,I will be unable to make it through\N the winter and will perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:05.82,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,There's no going back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:10.31,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,Do you now understand what you humans did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:16.23,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,My rage will not go away until I have killed\Na human for every child of mine they burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:21.06,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,If all else fails, I'll curse this land\N and use my hatred for you humans
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:23.12,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,to bring upon a never-ending curse of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.21,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,That's some insane miasma...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.75,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Is she turning into a tatarigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:34.78,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:37.12,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:42.64,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I'll spin the silk for you and\N take you to the Izumo festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.96,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to... take me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:47.65,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:54.28,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,What could you possibly do on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:58.78,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do this alone... But I have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.15,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,You humans will spin silk from my cocoons?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:15.38,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,You understand what will happen to this land\N if I do not make it to the festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:16.86,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:20.78,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:35.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wake up! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:41.32,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Someone to spin the silk, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:45.36,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to be able to get through\N all these cocoons by dawn, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:47.95,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have some brilliant plan, Arata?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:51.86,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea, so I'm going\N to hurry and look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:52.86,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,An idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:55.35,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back, so please get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:56.46,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.15,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't lose track of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.36,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:02.88,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,What do you people think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:05.64,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:06.97,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.23,sign_15992_171_MPD,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,MPD
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.23,sign_15992_172_Safety_First,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Safety First
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:24.62,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Senda, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:27.84,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you come here\N all the way from Kudanshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:29.63,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and just tell me where you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:31.67,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Could you start with\N the second-floor seats, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:47.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:50.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone from all the Nocturnal\N Community Relations Divisions are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:53.02,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So these are Oshira-sama's cocoons...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:55.31,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What time is dawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:58.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, 6:02.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:01.15,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So we have about thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.41,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,All right, lights on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:12.34,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let down your guard until we know\N that the Another's no longer a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:18.24,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,Is that jerk still going on about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:20.13,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Well, considering his position...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:23.81,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,He should quit preparing for something\N that may not happen and actually help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:31.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:33.27,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not dawn yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.66,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,The Ears of Sand are worthless after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:50.05,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:06.30,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I brought us some more spinners!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:09.05,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:22.46,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,You asked Anothers for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:23.60,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:25.95,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:30.08,Default,Taro,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:32.71,Default,Taro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:33.45,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:37.49,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:40.56,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,This is absurd! I can't even—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:44.84,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,If Miyako says it's okay, then it is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:45.97,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:47.23,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:56.73,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako-kun, could I get an\N explanation for the record?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:58.08,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:01.98,Flashback,taro,0000,0000,0000,,I have no obligation to help humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:06.99,Flashback,Taro,0000,0000,0000,,And humans are the ones who burned\Nthe cocoons and angered the Silkworm Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.47,Flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,You're exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:12.24,Flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can say to deny that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:17.75,Flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,But if Manari-sama becomes a tatarigami,\N you'll no longer be able to live here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:22.09,Flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that to happen\N because of something humans did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:25.78,Flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that I'm being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:29.89,Flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,But this is all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:35.35,Flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Tarobo-san,\Nmembers of the tengu clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.76,Flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Please lend me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:40.63,Flashback,Tengu,0000,0000,0000,,What do you guys wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:44.67,Flashback,Tengu,0000,0000,0000,,If the princess can't make the festival,\N there'll be all kinds of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:45.90,Flashback,Tengu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:50.51,Flashback,Tengu,0000,0000,0000,,The humans should get what they deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:54.67,Flashback,Tengu,0000,0000,0000,,But we might not be able to live here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:56.33,Flashback,Tengu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:14:59.56,Flashback,Taro,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:08.15,Flashback,Taro,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, gather up the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:09.80,Flashback,Taro,0000,0000,0000,,I have somewhere to go with Seimei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:15.28,Flashback,Taro,0000,0000,0000,,You can use all the help\N you can get right now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:16.86,Flashback,Taro,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to get Adiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:21.08,Flashback,Taro,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you, Seimei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:24.18,Flashback,Taro,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... Miyako Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:27.58,Flashback,Taro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you to help me out\N the next time I need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:30.24,Flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Tarobo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:32.12,Flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:38.62,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's how you got all these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.61,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean, they're Anothers. Not people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:48.00,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,So the tengu added some conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.96,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I know you said it was dangerous to negotiate,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:54.47,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,but I thought this was a great opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:16:00.77,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,There were times my emotions were\N swayed because of my Ears of Sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:04.47,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,And I know that they're not always\N useful, after some experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:06.65,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,and that negotiating can be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:11.67,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,But I also learned that our reasoning\N may not mean a thing to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:15.78,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,and the fact that even angels and tengu\N are pretty similar to us sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:18.81,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,By "us," you mean humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:23.53,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. So I want to speak\N to more Anothers like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:25.97,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to my Ears of Sand,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:29.55,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell what they're saying\N and even found out their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:34.02,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,If I can use the Ears to help us\N understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:35.98,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,and stop any more conflicts,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:39.47,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,then I think that might be my calling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.48,Default,Taro,0000,0000,0000,,Arata, come here for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:03.33,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,Anothers and humans together...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:06.38,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,This is truly an amazing sight to behold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:11.40,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this basically\Nprove that he's a threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:12.96,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,A threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:18.09,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he's already got the Aztec god\N of mischief following him around, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:20.72,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Probably a bit late to worry about that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:29.23,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I need to start changing like Arata, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:32.23,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,I can't change my outlook that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:33.98,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling contradictory?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:36.94,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Our distance between Anothers\N and our fear of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:43.45,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,You never know what'll happen to you\N with this job if you ever forget your fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:49.46,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,So I get why you do the things\N you do, Kanoichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:54.33,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,But the way Miyako tries to solve problems
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:57.12,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,allows me to see things\N I never thought I'd see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:18:01.22,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,This is something that only Miyako can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.85,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm counting on you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.26,Default,Taro,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it somehow worked out in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:41.77,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:08.41,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,They're imperfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:10.47,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:14.87,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,But... A promise is a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:20.43,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that happened...\N the sins you humans committed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:22.55,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:24.69,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:31.06,Default,Kaiko,0000,0000,0000,,But I shall forgive them for your sake, Seimei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:20:00.41,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Miyako Arata, Manari-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:02.32,Default,Hue,0000,0000,0000,,Arata!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:05.35,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:08.22,Default,Hue,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this! Isn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.90,Default,Hue,0000,0000,0000,,I made it with that silk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:12.48,Default,Hue,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it simply gorgeous?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.26,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:17.23,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,You have some nerve, after we risked \Nour lives spinning that silk...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:20.06,Default,Hue,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go to Izumo now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:21.20,Default,Cat,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.36,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:24.61,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're not a Japanese god!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:27.28,Default,Hue,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to some presents when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.12,Default,Cat,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.86,Default,Hue,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:36.17,Default,Taro,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're heading home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:38.53,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything, Tarobo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:39.63,Default,Tengu,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.01,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.51,Default,Tengu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:46.10,Default,Taro,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:51.27,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:56.02,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,There were just a lot of coincidences and\N somehow, everything worked out okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:21:03.06,Default,Kano,0000,0000,0000,,If you think that'll happen every time,\N you're in for a world of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:08.03,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,If I were alone, that might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:11.29,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,But my Nocturnal Community\N Relations Division
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:13.46,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,is a team of four.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:28.98,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work, Miyako-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:31.06,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Great job, Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.34,0:21:34.50,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:36.31,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:39.77,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone worked really hard,\N so let's go have a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.76,Default,Theo,0000,0000,0000,,Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:44.44,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the time, should\N we go to our usual place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:46.01,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Anywhere is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:50.04,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,City Hall's buying, so eat whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:51.93,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't forget the receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:55.65,Default,Senda,0000,0000,0000,,And the expenses will be\N under Kanoichi-kun's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:56.47,Default,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.37,0:23:35.32,Next_Ep_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}#12 "The Shinjuku Ward Nocturnal Community Relations Division"
